## fping  (affects modules: netaddr, dns, icmp, seqmap)

The `netaddr` module's address-selection logic, the `icmp` module (echo
codec, ICMP sockets and the paced ping engine) and the `seqmap` module
(sequence-number correlation map, after fping's seqmap.c) were extracted from
the authors' `zig-fping` project, which is a Zig port of fping
(https://github.com/schweikert/fping). fping's license therefore applies to
the derived portions and is reproduced here as its terms require:

    Original author:      Roland Schemers   <schemers@stanford.edu>
    IPv6 Support:         Jeroen Massar
